Package com.legacy.structure_gel.worldgen.jigsaw

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractGelStructurePiece
    An extension of AbstractVillagePiece for jigsaw structures that allows for data structure block interaction and contains more functional methods to go along with that.
    GelConfigJigsawStructure
    Extension of GelJigsawStructure for easy implementation of config files using ConfigTemplates.StructureConfig.
    GelJigsawPiece
    Extension of SingleJigsawPiece without the BlockIgnoreStructureProcessor.AIR_AND_STRUCTURE_BLOCK in favor of RemoveGelStructureProcessor.INSTANCE and including a way to determine interactions with water.
    GelJigsawStructure
    An extension of GelStructure to use with jigsaw structures.
    GelJigsawStructure.Start  
    GelStructurePiece
    The default implementation of AbstractGelStructurePiece.
    JigsawPoolBuilder
    Assists in the creation of jigsaw pools, allowing multiple pools to be created using the same settings.
    JigsawRegistryHelper
    Assists in the registry process for Jigsaw structures to shorten names and give shorter methods.
